@startuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
actor User
participant Frontend as FE
participant "Backend / AI Controller" as API
participant "Vector DB / Database" as DB
participant "LLM Provider (OpenAI/Gemini)" as LLM

User -> FE: Open Chatbot & Send Message
FE -> API: Send Message Request (Session ID, User ID, Message)
API -> DB: Fetch Chat History & Context
API -> DB: Fetch Relevant Store Data (Products, FAQs, Policies)
DB --> API: Context Data

API -> API: Construct Prompt (History + Context + Message)
API -> LLM: Generate Response
LLM --> API: AI Response Text
API -> DB: Save Assistant Response to History
API --> FE: Return Response

FE --> User: Display AI Message
@enduml
